comment:
* Collections of constants for internal tethering usage. * *

These hidden constants are not in TetheringManager as they are not part of the API stubs * generated for TetheringManager, which prevents the tethering module from linking them at * build time. * TODO: investigate changing the tethering build rules so that Tethering can reference hidden * symbols from framework-tethering even when they are in a non-hidden class. * @hide

variables.name: EXTRA_ADD_TETHER_TYPE
variables.comment:
* Extra used for communicating with the TetherService and TetherProvisioningActivity.
     * Includes the type of tethering to enable if any.

variables.name: EXTRA_REM_TETHER_TYPE
variables.comment:
* Extra used for communicating with the TetherService. Includes the type of tethering for
     * which to cancel provisioning.

variables.name: EXTRA_SET_ALARM
variables.comment:
* Extra used for communicating with the TetherService. True to schedule a recheck of tether
     * provisioning.

variables.name: EXTRA_RUN_PROVISION
variables.comment: * Tells the TetherService to run a provision check now.

variables.name: EXTRA_PROVISION_CALLBACK
variables.comment:
* Extra used for communicating with the TetherService and TetherProvisioningActivity.
     * Contains the {@link ResultReceiver} which will receive provisioning results.
     * Can not be empty.

variables.name: EXTRA_TETHER_SUBID
variables.comment:
* Extra used for communicating with the TetherService and TetherProvisioningActivity.
     * Contains the subId of current active cellular upstream.
     * @hide

variables.name: EXTRA_TETHER_UI_PROVISIONING_APP_NAME
variables.comment:
* Extra used for telling TetherProvisioningActivity the entitlement package name and class
     * name to start UI entitlement check.
     * @hide

variables.name: EXTRA_TETHER_SILENT_PROVISIONING_ACTION
variables.comment:
* Extra used for telling TetherService the intent action to start silent entitlement check.
     * @hide

variables.name: EXTRA_TETHER_PROVISIONING_RESPONSE
variables.comment:
* Extra used for TetherService to receive the response of provisioning check.
     * @hide
